      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0025",
      "text": "Registered State Change Notification (RSCN)",
      "bbox": [
        133.74,
        514.96,
        347.56,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0026",
      "text": "4.2.18.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        195.92,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0027",
      "text": "A RSCN ELS shall be sent to registered Nx_Ports when an event occurs that may have affected the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        540.03,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0028",
      "text": "state of one or more Nx_Ports, or the ULP state within the Nx_Port.  The term state is used here to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.93,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0029",
      "text": "refer to any condition of an Nx_Port that is considered important enough to notify other Nx_Ports of a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.02,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0030",
      "text": "change in that state.  The definition of important is specific to an Nx_Port implementation, but should",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        539.93,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0031",
      "text": "include the Login state or Link state.  The RSCN additionally provides an indication of the change of",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        540.02,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0032",
      "text": "state that is being reported.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        217.1,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0033",
      "text": "RSCN is intended to provide a timely indication of changes in nodes to avoid the considerable traffic",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.07,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0034",
      "text": "that polling may generate.  RSCN may be used to indicate a failed node, allowing the release of re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        540.02,
        670.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0035",
      "text": "sources tied up by the failed node.  RSCN may also be used to notify interested nodes of new devic-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        540.24,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p064_s0036",
      "text": "es coming online, and of changes within an online node that affect the operation of the system (e.g.,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        539.93,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
